      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>You fix broken objects and artificial life forms with ease</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Int 13, Engineering 5 ranks</p><hr /><p><strong>Benefit:</strong> You can use Engineering to perform the @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.GMkLZsN3a7YPvA03.JournalEntryPage.d4fcGwOcrsuYrwGH#treat-deadly-wounds]{treat wounds} task of Medicine on constructs, substituting a tool kit for a medical kit and a workshop for a medical bay and restoring Hit Points on a success equal to your Intelligence modifier. When you successfully use Engineering to repair objects, you restore additional Hit Points equal to double your intelligence modifier. ([[/ floor(@abilities.int.mod * 2)]])</p>"
